text: Mylène de Zoete (born 3 January 1999) is a Dutch road and track cyclist. She is a member of the Dutch women's road bicycle racing team AG Insurance–NXTG since 2020. As a track cyclist she represents the Netherlans at international tournaments. De Zoete won the bronze medal in the elimination race event at the 2022 UEC European Track Championships.
